This sample showcases the RowStyle capability of GridDataControl. 
The GridDataControl appearance can be enhanced in different ways, such as row styles, conditional formats, table options, and visual styles. 
Row styles are used for row-wise formatting. Conditional formats apply formatting only when a given criteria are met. 
Table options feature various options available to customize a table. 
Visual styles list the built-in themes supported by the GridDataControl. 
